	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St. Thomas</placeName> <date>Feby 3. 5608</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isc Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">It is really a long while since that I have<lb/> had this pleasure but absence has prevented my attention<lb/> ere this to your various favors&#59; every thing is right except<lb/> the pack of Occidents for <date>October</date> which did not come by the<lb/> Emily altho&#39; your letter said so&#44; <persName>Captain Davis</persName> says that<lb/> no such pack came on board.  I intend to make you a<lb/> shipment of Bay Water in a short time&#44; &#38; will see if accounts<lb/> can&#39;t be squared&#44; I have not sold a single <sic>sett</sic> of Parasah<lb/> or Prayer books since my last&#59; I have disposed of 3 Prayer<lb/> Books  Oblige me &#38; let me know the names of those for<lb/> whom I ordered the Pentateuch.  I am not yet paid by some<lb/> I write this evening to <persName>James Henry Esq</persName> at <placeName>New York</placeName> for<lb/> Matzot&#44; if they bake early in <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> &#40;say earlier<lb/> than <placeName>N York</placeName>&#44; the baker can send to him for me 4 Cases<lb/> each 25 <add>&#63;</add> Matzot &#38; 2 Setts Shemurim it would be necessary<lb/> to inform him of such intention that he does not engage<lb/> any for me&#44; he is limited to <date>24th March</date> to ship</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">Wishing you health &#38; success</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">I am Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Your Obedt Servt</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">M B Simmons</persName></p>
				<p><placeName>Charleston</placeName> wants what it will not obtain&#44; such is my idea as<lb/> &#36;1000 is not an inducement for such a scholar.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><addressee>Revd Isc Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">via <placeName>N. York</placeName></p>
				<p rend="The following written on the back of the envelope."></p>
				<p>Respt yours &#38; your obt ser.</p>
				<p><persName>Elijah</persName>. Dr <add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Wilmington</placeName>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">N.C.</hi></placeName></p>
		</body>
